main(String[]) - Static method in class shell.distance.GMapShell
Executes this program by this following command: java -cp $CLASSPATH:$main_jarfile shell.distance.GMapShell --apiKey AIza..YOUR_OWN_API-KEY...; whereas $CLASSPATH contains all required .jar files okhttp-2.2.0.jar gson-2.3.1.jar joda-time-2.7.jar gmapservice.jar okio.jar $main_jarfile and $main_jarfile is the actual .jar file (in the current version (since February 2015, it's called gshellmap.jar) which contains shell/GMapShell.class.
main(String[]) - Static method in class shell.geometry.GooMetryShell
Excutes this program by this following command: java -cp $CLASSPATH:$main_jarfile shell.geometry.GooMetryShell --apiKey AiZa...YOUR_OWN_API-KEY --latitude $v1 --longitude $v2, whereas $v1 and $v2 are degree values.
v1=[-90.000000, 90.000000]
v2=[-179.999999, 180.000000]
If you need help, type --help right after the class name (in this case "shell.geometry.GooMetryShell")
main(String[]) - Static method in class shell.mysql.GPhonebook
Executes this program by this following command: java -cp $CLASSPATH:$main_jarfile shell.mysql.GPhonebook --apiKey YOUR_API-KEY --query [all|address|mail|phone] $CLASSPATH contains: okhttp-2.2.0.jar gson-2.3.1.jar joda-time-2.7.jar mysql-connector-java-5.1.34-bin.jar gmapservice.jar okio.jar $main_jarfile Type --help for help information
